     H            Y.
     F** ATBR31 ****************************
     F* PART NO APPOINTMENT INTRAL COMPANY SERVICE SCHEDULE INVESTIGATION LIST
     F*  < APPOINTMENT DATA CHECK>
     F* A-IDOTA 1993.10.13 *
     F**************************** ATBR31 **
     FATBPW31 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FAGAPL31 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
     FATBWP31 IF  E           K        DISK                      A
     E                    ER      1  10 60
      *品番*
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 @HIN
     I                                        1   5 @HIN1
     I                                        6  10 @HIN2
     I                                       11  12 @HIN3
      *発行日・便*
     I            DS
     I                                        1  100@HKO
     I                                        1   40@HYY
     I                                        5   60@HMM
     I                                        7   80@HDD
     I                                        9  100@HBN
      * KEY *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @HIN1
     C                     KFLD           @HIN2
     C                     KFLD           @HIN3
      *
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @HYY
     C                     KFLD           @HMM
     C                     KFLD           @HDD
      *
     C           KEY3      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @HIN
     C                     KFLD           @HKO
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @HIN
      ************
      *初期設定*
      ************
     C           STP10     TAG
     C                     SETOF                     010299
     C                     SETOF                     KE
     C                     SETON                     70
     C                     Z-ADD0         @HKO
      ************
      *画面入力*
      ************
     C           STP20     TAG
     C                     EXFMTATBPW311
      * END *
     C           *INKA     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     END
      *
     C                     SETOF                     010299
     C                     SETOF                     70
      ************
      *社内品番*
      ************
     C           @HIN1     IFEQ *BLANK
     C           @HIN2     ANDEQ*BLANK
     C           @HIN3     ANDEQ*BLANK
     C                     MOVELER,1      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
      *平準化確定発注ファイル*
     C                     SETOF                     30
     C           KEY1      CHAINAGAPL311             30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '0'
     C           CBSKJY    ANDEQ'D'
     C           CBSKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     30
     C                     END
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVELER,2      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
      **************
      *発行日・便*
      **************
     C           @HYY      IFEQ 0
     C           @HMM      ANDEQ0
     C           @HDD      ANDEQ0
     C           @HBN      ANDEQ0
     C                     MOVELER,3      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
      *論理チェック*
     C           @HYY      IFLT 93
     C                     MOVELER,4      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
     C           @HMM      IFLE 0
     C           @HMM      ORGT 12
     C                     MOVELER,5      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
     C           @HDD      IFLE 0
     C           @HDD      ORGT 31
     C                     MOVELER,6      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
     C           @HBN      IFEQ 0
     C                     MOVELER,7      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
      *青山カレンダー・ファイル*
     C                     SETOF                     30
     C           KEY2      CHAINAGDPL121             30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVELER,8      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
      *
     C           F8HIRU    IFEQ '*'
     C           F8YORU    ANDEQ'*'
     C                     MOVELER,9      MSG
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
      *重複チェック*
     C                     SETOF                     30
     C           KEY3      CHAINATBWP311             30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVELER,10     MSG
     C                     SETON                     010299
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
      *
     C           *INKE     IFEQ '0'
     C                     GOTO STP20
     C                     END
      ************
      *登録処理*
      ************
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    ATHINB
     C                     Z-ADD0         ATHAKO
     C                     MOVEL@HIN      ATHINB
     C                     Z-ADD@HKO      ATHAKO
     C                     WRITEATBWP311
     C                     SETON                     U1
     C                     GOTO STP10
**  ERR-MSG
E-01 INPUT INTRAL COMPANY PART NO
E-02 LEVEL PROD FIXED ORDERING FILE DOESN'T INCLUDE IT
E-03  INPUT PUBLICATION DATE BIN.
E-04  THE INPUT OF YEAR IS NOT RIGHT
E-05 THE INPUT OF MONTH IS NOT RIGHT
E-06 THE INPUT OF DAY IS NOT RIGHT
E-07 THE INPUT OF BIN IS NOT RIGHT
E-08 AOYAMA CALENDAR FILE DOESN'T INCLUDE IT.
E-09 AOYAMA IS A HOLIDAY
E-10 THIS PART NO AND PUBLICATION DATE ARE ALREADY INPUT.
